{"word":"ἱζάνω","slug":"ἱζάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἱζάνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἵζω'><el>ἵζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>Causal, <i>to make to sit</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to sit</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>sedere</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>ἐπ' ὄμμασι ὕπνος ἱζάνει</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of soil, <i>to settle down, sink in</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}